<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
    <!--Import Google Icon Font-->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--Import materialize.css-->
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/materialize.min.css" media="screen,projection" />

    <!--Let browser know website is optimized for mobile-->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- Compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/css/materialize.min.css">

    <!-- Compiled and minified JavaScript -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/js/materialize.min.js"></script>

    <title>Murph's Meat-Up</title>

</head>

<body>
    <h1>Murph's Meat-Up™</h1>

    <!-- Navbar goes here -->

    <!-- Page Layout here -->
    <div class="row">

        <div class="col s12 m4 l3">
            <!-- Note that "m4 l3" was added -->
            <!-- Grey navigation panel

              This content will be:
          3-columns-wide on large screens,
          4-columns-wide on medium screens,
          12-columns-wide on small screens  -->

        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m7">
            <h2 class="header"></h2>
            <div class="card horizontal">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="images/bbq.jpg">
                </div>
                <div class="card-stacked">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Here is a picture from the last Murph's Meat-Up™. As you can see, we take the tradional art of grilling,
                            and place it firmly in the good ol' Southern USA. As we say down here in these parts, "One man's
                            junk is another man's source of dinner. Oh, and cold beer." If you would love to add your name
                            to the next Meat-Up™, than click the link below and add yourself to the list!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-action">
                        <a href="#">Sign me up NOW!!!</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Note that "m8 l9" was added -->
        <!-- Teal page content

              This content will be:
          9-columns-wide on large screens,
          8-columns-wide on medium screens,
          12-columns-wide on small screens  -->

    </div>

    </div>

    <table class="highlight">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Name:</th>
                <th>Gender:</th>
                <th>Meat:</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
            <tr>
                {{#each attendee}}
                <li>
                    <a href="/user/{{_id}}">{{name}}</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/user/{{_id}}">{{gender}}</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/user/{{_id}}">{{meat}}</a>
                </li>
                {{/each}}
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>

    <!--Import jQuery before materialize.js-->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/materialize.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>